74
00:13:02.510 --> 00:13:07.910
- Da-mi cheile.
- Nimeni nu-mi conduce masina decat eu.


75
00:13:08.210 --> 00:13:12.910
Stiu, iubitule, dar Regina Croaker
trebuie sa se duca acasa acum.


76
00:13:13.210 --> 00:13:17.310
- Hei, voi doi.
- Da-mi cheile.


77
00:13:17.710 --> 00:13:22.310
Vino in spate cu mine.
Te voi lasa sa-mi faci unele lucruri.


78
00:13:22.710 --> 00:13:27.210
- Nimeni nu-mi conduce masina decat eu.
- Urca in masina.


79
00:13:41.010 --> 00:13:44.810
Nu poti conduce pe degeaba.

80
00:13:45.610 --> 00:13:49.410
Poti sa spui "alcoolic"?

81
00:13:54.610 --> 00:13:58.510
Ce dracu-i porcaria asta?

82
00:14:15.810 --> 00:14:17.910
Ce-i cu tine?

83
00:14:19.210 --> 00:14:21.510
Ai grija!

84
00:14:29.310 --> 00:14:32.510
- Ce a fost asta?
